{"lemma":"عَرِيكَةٌ","slug":"عَرِيكَةٌ","root":"ع.ر.ك","root_slug":"ع-ر-ك","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ر-ك","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n28818"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%83%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28818","headword_ar":"عَرِيكَةٌ","root":"Erk","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A camel's hump:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"remainder thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eariykapu Als~anaAmi","text_ar":"عَرِيكَةُ السَّنَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what remains of the hump:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, S, O:) so called because the purchaser feels that part ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaEorukuhu","text_ar":"يَعْرُكُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":") to know the fatness and strength [of the animal]: (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaraAy^iku","text_ar":"عَرَايِكُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; which is said by some to signify the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"humps with the backs."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.) ―         -b2-  [Hence, in phrases here following,] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Nature; natural, native,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"innate, disposition"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"temper"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soul, spirit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mind."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN lay~inu AlEariykapi","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ لَيِّنُ العَرِيكَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is easy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gentle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in natural disposition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"submissive, tractable;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * O, * TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one whose pride,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"haughtiness, has been broken,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"subdued;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having little contrariness and aversion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$adiydu AlEariykapi","text_ar":"شَدِيدُ العَرِيكَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strong in spirit, incompliant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resisting:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laAnato","text_ar":"لَانَتْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eariykatuhu","text_ar":"عَرِيكَتُهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His pride,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"haughtiness, became broken,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"subdued:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) originally relating to the camel; for they used to betake themselves to the camel when he had the disposition of refusing to be ridden or mounted, and incompliance, and cut [a part] in his hump, it being high, difficult to ride upon; and when this was done, he became quiet, and was rendered inclinable, and the part of him that was the place of riding became easy to sit upon; so one said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qado laAnato Eariykatuhu","text_ar":"قَدْ لَانَتْ عَرِيكَتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har pp. 566-7.) One says also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN mayomuwnu AlEariykapi","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ مَيْمُونُ العَرِيكَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man fortunate, happy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blest, in natural disposition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in mind."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","ISk","S","O","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}